-- Somfy Agrees to Sell Agta Record Stake to Assa Abloy for 25 Euros a Share
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-18T05:54:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/somfy-agrees-to-sell-agta-record-stake-to-assa-abloy-for-25-euros-a-share.html
Somfy SA said it has agreed to sell
its 32.95 percent stake in Agta Record to Assa Abloy AB for 25
euros a share.  The news came in an emailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  